O meriri ihe nrite ọlaọcha na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị nke kilogram iri ise na ise na afọ puku abụọ na iri abụo na otu na World Weightlifting Championships nke emere na Tashkent, Uzbekistan. Ọ nọchitere anya Naijiria na 2019 Egwuregwu Afrịka nke bụkwa ihe ngosi mbụ ya n'egwuregwu Afrịka ma kwuo na ọ bụ ihe nrite atọ gụnyere ihe nrite ọla edo abụọ na ihe omume ibu nke ụmụ nwanyị kilogram iri ise na ise.

O kwuru na o nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo na 55 kilogram na 55 kilogram mmeme clean jerk nke ụmụ nwanyị tinyere ọlaọcha na 55 kilogram mmeme snatch ebe ọ fọrọ nke nta ka onye obodo ya bụ Chika Amalaha nweta ihe nrite ego ọla edo. Otú ọ dị, ọ pụtara dị ka onye nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị 55 kilogram n'ozuzu ya ebe Chika Amalaha kwenyere maka ihe nrite ego ọlaọcha. N'abalị iri abụọ na isii n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 2019, Adijat mepụtara ihe ndekọ ọhụrụ nke Afrịka n'ịbu ibu dị arọ n'ụdị dị ọcha na nke na-agba ọsọ site n'ibuli kilogram 116 n'oge 2019 African Games.
Na 2022 Commonwealth Games nke emere na Birmingham, UK, ọ nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo na ihe egwuregwu Records abụọ ọhụrụ: 92kg na snatch na 203kg n'ozuzu.Àtụ:Notelist
